Are you a wizard at extracting data from websites? Do you have the skills to navigate through complex sites to retrieve information efficiently? If yes, we want you on our team! We're seeking a highly skilled and detail-oriented Virtual Assistant who is an expert in data scraping.


Key Responsibilities:

- Scrape data from specified websites in a structured and organized manner.
- Ensure the accuracy and quality of extracted data.
- Regularly update and maintain databases with new information.
- Provide insights and recommendations based on data analysis.
- Troubleshoot any issues related to data scraping.
- Collaborate with our team to meet project goals and deadlines.


Requirements:

- Proven experience in data scraping.
- Familiarity with scraping tools and software.
- Strong understanding of data privacy and security measures.
- Excellent attention to detail.
- Ability to work independently and meet deadlines.
- Good communication skills and proficiency in English.
